{{Infobox brain|Name=大脑半球|Latin=Hemisphaerium cerebri|Image=Blausen 0215 CerebralHemispheres.png|Caption=人类的[[脑|脑]] （前方视角）|Image2=Cerebral hemisphere - animation.gif|Caption2={{Legend|#F270F4|右脑半球}}{{Legend|#7086F4|左脑半球}}|IsPartOf=|Components=|Artery=|Vein=}}'''大脑半球'''（英文：Cerebral hemisphere）是[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]][[大脑|大脑]]的基本结构，一个大脑由两个大脑半球组成（分左右），其中有[[中央縱裂|中央纵裂]]隔开<ref name="#1">{{Cite book|chapter=Neuroanatomy, Cerebral Hemisphere|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK549789/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=31747196|first=Toai|last=Bui|first2=Joe|last2=M Das|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2022-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220413154119/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK549789/}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Interhemispheric fissure {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/interhemispheric-fissure?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-06|last=Muzio|first=Bruno Di|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201110041616/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/interhemispheric-fissure?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[真兽下纲|真兽下纲]]的[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]中，两个大脑半球由[[胼胝体|胼胝体]]连接，后者中含有大量[[神经纤维|神经纤维]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Neuroscience For Kids - Hemispheres|url=https://faculty.washington.edu/chudler/split.html|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=[[华盛顿大学|华盛顿大学]]|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210206224528/https://faculty.washington.edu/chudler/split.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|chapter=Neuroanatomy, Corpus Callosum|title=StatPearls|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK448209/|publisher=StatPearls Publishing|date=2021|location=Treasure Island (FL)|pmid=28846239|first=Andrea|last=Goldstein|first2=Benjamin P.|last2=Covington|first3=Navid|last3=Mahabadi|first4=Fassil B.|last4=Mesfin|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2022-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220207035104/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK448209/}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Commissural Fiber - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/commissural-fiber|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716193508/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/commissural-fiber|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，在所有脊椎动物中，存在比胼胝体更小的脑部连合（commissure）连接着左右大脑半球，包括[[前连合|前连合]]、[[后连合|后连合]]、[[腦穹窿|脑穹窿]]等<ref name=":0" />。这些连合在左右半球间传递信息、起协调功能<ref name=":0" />。

== 内部结构 ==
[[File:Poles_of_cerebral_hemispheres_(en)_-_inferiror_view.png|链接=https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Poles_of_cerebral_hemispheres_(en)_-_inferiror_view.png]]
每个大脑半球的[[大脑皮层|皮层]]由[[灰质|灰质]]构成，由一层[[白质|白质]]支撑（{{le|半卵圆中心|Centrum semiovale}}）<ref name="Neurology">{{cite journal|title=Centrum ovale infarcts: subcortical infarction in the superficial territory of the middle cerebral artery.|first1=J|last2=Regli|first2=F|date=October 1992|journal=Neurology|issue=10|doi=10.1212/wnl.42.10.1992|volume=42|pages=1992–8|pmid=1340771|last1=Bogousslavsky}}</ref>。大脑半球的内部包括[[侧脑室|侧脑室]]、[[基底核|基底核]]以及白质<ref name="isbn0-7817-9427-7">{{cite book|author=Snell, Richard S.|title=Clinical Neuroanatomy (Clinical Neuroanatomy for Medical Students (Snell))|publisher=Lippincott Williams & Wilkins|location=Hagerstwon, MD|year=2009|pages=262|isbn=978-0-7817-9427-5}}</ref>。

大脑半球中存在四个基本区域：[[额叶|额叶]]、[[颞叶|颞叶]]、[[顶叶|顶叶]]、[[枕叶|枕叶]]<ref name="#1"/>。其中的三极（poles）或终端（ends）位于额叶、颞叶和枕叶<ref>{{Cite web|title=Poles of cerebral hemispheres {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/poles-of-cerebral-hemispheres?lang=us#:~:text=The%20brain%20has%20three%20pointed,anterior%20end%20of%20the%20hemisphere&text=the%20occipital%20pole%20corresponds%20to%20the%20posterior%20end%20of%20the%20hemisphere|accessdate=2021-03-06|last=Muzio|first=Bruno Di|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US}}</ref>： 额极（frontal pole）、颞极（temporal pole）、枕极（occipital pole）。[[中央沟|中央沟]]将[[顶叶|顶叶]]和额叶分隔开，并将[[初级运动皮层|初级运动皮层]]和{{le|初级体感皮层|Primary somatosensory cortex}}隔开<ref>{{Cite web|title=Central Sulcus - an overview|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/central-sulcus|accessdate=2021-03-06|work=|publisher=Science Direct|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927182131/http://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/neuroscience/central-sulcus|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Central sulcus {{!}} Radiology Reference Article {{!}} Radiopaedia.org|url=https://radiopaedia.org/articles/central-sulcus?lang=us|accessdate=2021-03-06|last=Elgendy|first=Azza|work=Radiopaedia|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201114091803/https://radiopaedia.org/articles/central-sulcus?lang=us|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 半球对比 ==
宏观而言，两个大脑半球之间互为粗略镜像，只存在少许差别，譬如人脑中的{{le|雅科夫列夫扭矩|Yakovlevian torque}}（右侧半球轻微向左扭进）<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Cerebral Asymmetry: A Quantitative, Multifactorial, and Plastic Brain Phenotype|url=https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/twin-research-and-human-genetics/article/cerebral-asymmetry-a-quantitative-multifactorial-and-plastic-brain-phenotype/6B69E8EF4FC75A0B851C9A606A5BE1E0|last=Rentería|first=Miguel E.|date=2012/06|journal=Twin Research and Human Genetics|issue=3|doi=10.1017/thg.2012.13|volume=15|pages=401–413|language=en|issn=1839-2628|access-date=2021-03-06|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613163048/https://www.cambridge.org/core/journals/twin-research-and-human-genetics/article/cerebral-asymmetry-a-quantitative-multifactorial-and-plastic-brain-phenotype/6B69E8EF4FC75A0B851C9A606A5BE1E0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。微观而言，两个半球间在{{le|细胞架构|Cytoarchitecture}}、细胞功能、[[神经递质|神经递质]]以及[[受体_(生物化学)|受体]]种类上存在显著不对称<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Age and hemisphere effects on dendritic structure|url=https://doi.org/10.1093/brain/119.6.1983|last=Anderson|first=Britt|last2=Rutledge|first2=Valisa|date=1996-12-01|journal=Brain|issue=6|doi=10.1093/brain/119.6.1983|volume=119|pages=1983–1990|issn=0006-8950}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hemispheric asymmetries in cerebral cortical networks|url=https://www.cell.com/trends/neurosciences/abstract/S0166-2236(03)00198-X|last=Hutsler|first=Jeffrey|last2=Galuske|first2=Ralf A. W.|date=2003-08-01|journal=Trends in Neurosciences|issue=8|doi=10.1016/S0166-2236(03)00198-X|volume=26|pages=429–435|language=en|issn=0166-2236|pmid=12900174|access-date=2021-04-03|archive-date=2013-10-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016074307/http://www.cell.com/trends/neurosciences/abstract/S0166-2236(03)00198-X|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

尽管左右大脑半球间的部分差异在人群中普遍存在，甚至在不同物种中也存在，但许多差异在同个物种的不同个体中依然有程度之分。

